        <updateDate>2018-07-11T20:46:27Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p> This bill requires the Department of Transportation to conduct a study to determine how many employees who must comply with the electronic logging device requirements have ceased being operators of a commercial motor vehicle as a result of such requirements.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
